        <Parent_String>tables by form: base form [300039578], tables by form [300039928], tables (support furniture) [300039548], support furniture [300039337], furniture by form or function [300048628], furniture [300037680], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
